high_descs: Turn left and walk six steps and turn left and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the far right, green spray bottle from the top of the toilet tank,
Turn around and take one step forward, turn left for one step, turn left again and walk over to the trash can.
Put the spray bottle in the top left of the trash can with the nozzle pointing straight ahead.
Turn left for one step, turn left and walk to the counter by the sink.
Pick up the green spray bottle.
Turn around and walk over to the trash can.
Put the spray bottle in the trash can in front of the bottle already there, with the nozzle to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk to the toilet on the left.
Pick up the spray bottle on the right from the back of the toilet.
Move to face the black bin to the right of the toilet.
Put the spray bottle down in the black bin.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spray bottle to the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk back over to the black bin.
Place the spray bottle inside of the black bin.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the black bin.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk over to the right side of the toilet ahead
grab a spray bottle off of the top of the toilet
move to the right a bit and face the garbage bin in the corner of the room
place the spray bottle down inside of the garbage bin
turn around and walk over to the sink up ahead
grab a spray bottle off of the sink counter on the left
turn around and walk back over to the garbage bin in the corner of the room
place the spray bottle down inside of the garbage bin
